{"word":"H6465 - פְּעֹור - Pᵉʻôwr - peh-ore' - Peor","slug":"H6465","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">פְּעֹור</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Pᵉʻôwr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>peh-ore'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Peor"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05E2;&#x05D5;&#x05E8; - p<sup>e</sup>&#x201B;o&#x0302;r</b> - <i>peh-ore'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H6473\">H6473</a>; a <i>gap</i>; <i>Peor</i>, a mountain East of Jordan; also (for <a href=\"#/H1187\">H1187</a>) a deity worshipped there: - Peor. See also <a href=\"#/H1047\">H1047</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6473\">H6473</a>, <a href=\"#/H6474\">H6474</a>"}]}